<plot>Douglas is a recovering amnesiac stroke victim, who finds himself at the center of a documentary following his search for his long lost niece. However, the unscrupulous filmmakers feel that their documentary is too boring, so they hire an actress to play Douglas' niece, newly returned from abroad... This dark satire illustrates what happens when documentary filmmakers go bad.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?157834</url></doc>
